message: 1、写卡功能支持更多cuid白卡。||2、修复Android 14上钱包和快捷方式模拟卡片导致闪退的bug。||3、修复卡片的圆角在不同设备上显示不一致的bug。||4、修复已知bug
message_en: 1、The card writing function supports more cuid cards.||2、Fix the bug that caused the wallet and shortcut to simulate the card on Android 14 to crash.||3、Fixed the bug where the rounded corners of the card are displayed inconsistently on different devices.||4. General stability & performance improvements.
